{"tid":352142,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)銀河守護隊1-2","createTime":"2017-08-08T14:50:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-08T19:11:10.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"93b86112beb21be9ef31311fd801c0e7120dbba6","tid":352142,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T14:50:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=IPeb%2FL5o4%2FBGP0ASBIh8kY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=04d307ea\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=IPeb%2FL5o4%2FBGP0ASBIh8kY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=92ec4a73\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有dailymotion<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=IPeb%2FL5o4%2FBGP0ASBIh8kY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=ffd751ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/e/ed/Guardians_of_the_galaxy_ver2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fe%2Fed%2FGuardians_of_the_galaxy_ver2.jpg&h=c1d9b6ea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/6/6b/Guardians_of_the_Galaxy_Vol._2_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F6%2F6b%2FGuardians_of_the_Galaxy_Vol._2_Poster.jpg&h=63101220&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.beautimode.com/medias/1afdd4d6a08230d51e91a6119f155822.jpg/360\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.beautimode.com%2Fmedias%2F1afdd4d6a08230d51e91a6119f155822.jpg%2F360&h=3c89a678&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.1988年，年幼喪母的彼得&middot;奎爾被以勇度為首的太空海盜組織「掠奪者」綁架。26年後奎爾在莫拉格星（Morag）盜走「宇宙靈球」（Orb[註 1]）時，被對克里人狂熱的羅南的下屬「追尋者」加羅斯逮捕。儘管奎爾帶著靈球逃跑，但勇度發現了他的盜竊發行，發布刺客聯盟，羅南則派遣刺客葛摩菈追回靈球<br />\n<br />\n2.2014年，星爵、葛摩菈、德克斯、火箭浣熊和小格魯特以「星際異攻隊」的稱號聲名鵲起。至高族（Sovereign）的領袖阿耶莎同護衛隊的成員進行了一場交易，後者要從跨次元的怪物中保護珍貴的電池免遭損壞，作為回報，阿耶莎會把葛摩菈的妹妹涅布拉交給他們，涅布拉在試圖偷走電池時被至高族抓獲，在護衛隊要離開前，阿耶莎對於星爵為人類與未知外星族混血表示厭惡。離開索維林星不久因為火箭偷偷地拿走電池的一部分，索維林人便操縱無人飛船艦隊襲擊護衛隊<br />\n<br />\n11 25PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=IPeb%2FL5o4%2FBGP0ASBIh8kY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=e1024ae6\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=IPeb%2FL5o4%2FBGP0ASBIh8kY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=573b305b\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70b2562b619063135b6cc3e37c63b84080616a6f","tid":352142,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T14:53:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.